    { questionText: "What is a series of arches combined side by side into a repeating architectural pattern called?", correctAnswer: "An arcade", options: ["An arcade", "A barrel vault", "A flying buttress", "A curtain wall"], explanation: "Combining multiple arches side by side creates an arcade, used in bridges and building facades.", hint: "This repeating pattern of arches shares its name with a place full of games today." }
